  "notes": "Per-hole par, stroke index, and all four tee distances confirmed identically by RFEG and the club's official scorecard PDF. Layout is 8 par 4s + 10 par 3s (no par 5s), par 31 out / 31 in. Two misprints on the club PDF resolved in favor of RFEG and the PDF's own totals: (1) PDF prints Blue TOTAL as 2680, but its per-hole Blue values sum to 2860 (1443 out + 1417 in), matching RFEG; (2) PDF prints Red hole 9 as 121, but its Red OUT total of 1306 requires 128, matching RFEG. Azules is rated only for women; Rojas is rated for both genders (M 56.3/64, F 58.1/89 — assignment follows RFEG and the expected pattern that the short 2559 m course rates lower for men). Stroke index is the single allocation printed for all tees. Distances sum exactly to published totals; SI is a permutation of 1-18."
